  "title": "Kitchen Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome and greet customers warmly to ensure a positive Peranakan dining experience. </li><li>Take customer orders accurately, serve food and beverages promptly.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness, organize of services and hygienic dining areas.</li><li>Carry out other ad hoc duties as assigned by the manager or supervisor.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Work Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>10am -10pm (6 days per week).</li><li>1 off day during Monday to Thursday.</li><li>work in Orchard area.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Have a good and high standard in health, safety and hygiene.</li><li>Able to work on weekends & public holidays.</li><li>Able to work well in a team and provide excellent customer service. </li></ul>",
